1
00:00:06,260 --> 00:00:09,190
At this point,
don't you have even a trace of remorse?

2
00:00:09,300 --> 00:00:10,500
Remorse?

3
00:00:11,780 --> 00:00:13,910
That's something only fools possess,

4
00:00:14,620 --> 00:00:16,420
especially fools like you!

5
00:00:17,220 --> 00:00:18,860
You only think of others.

6
00:00:19,300 --> 00:00:20,180
How pitiful.

7
00:00:23,700 --> 00:00:24,580
Do you know...

8
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:28,860
what your father said to me
before he died?

9
00:00:31,400 --> 00:00:32,380
Please...

10
00:00:34,440 --> 00:00:35,200
report...

11
00:00:35,560 --> 00:00:36,760
to...

12
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:37,920
the Emperor...

13
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:39,800
that in Bronze County,

14
00:00:40,240 --> 00:00:41,480
Young Master Gao...

15
00:00:41,680 --> 00:00:42,740
and the magistrate

16
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:45,040
are in collusion,

17
00:00:45,880 --> 00:00:47,720
tyrannizing the people there.

18
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:52,300
Please beg His Majesty...

19
00:00:52,860 --> 00:00:55,940
to seek justice...

20
00:00:57,420 --> 00:00:58,420
for the people...

21
00:01:00,620 --> 00:01:01,620
of Bronze County.

22
00:01:06,700 --> 00:01:09,620
I've never seen such a foolish person.

23
00:01:10,740 --> 00:01:11,900
At death's door,

24
00:01:11,900 --> 00:01:13,700
he was still thinking of others.

25
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:16,340
What did he want?

26
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:20,900
What did he want?

27
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:25,240
He wanted peace of mind.

28
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:29,220
He wanted to sleep soundly.

29
00:01:30,580 --> 00:01:33,460
He wanted to enjoy every meal.

30
00:01:35,780 --> 00:01:38,900
The rose's in her hand,
the flavor in mine—

31
00:01:39,900 --> 00:01:42,380
that's something venal people like you

32
00:01:42,900 --> 00:01:44,700
will never understand.

33
00:01:46,460 --> 00:01:48,660
You can ignore others' suffering,

34
00:01:49,700 --> 00:01:53,100
but you have no right
to mock those who help others in need!

35
00:01:54,660 --> 00:01:56,600
If this world is to be better,

36
00:01:57,620 --> 00:01:59,620
there has to be more people like them

37
00:02:00,460 --> 00:02:01,920
and fewer people like you!

38
00:02:08,020 --> 00:02:09,380
How touching.

39
00:02:10,259 --> 00:02:12,700
I was almost moved by you.

40
00:02:14,260 --> 00:02:15,780
Gongsun Hao,

41
00:02:15,780 --> 00:02:18,020
if you have any humanity left,

42
00:02:19,140 --> 00:02:20,100
please...

43
00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:22,340
tell me...

44
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:25,500
where my father's body is.

45
00:02:26,820 --> 00:02:28,180
Please.

46
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:33,020
Have you heard of...

47
00:02:33,380 --> 00:02:35,060
corpse-dissolving liquid?

48
00:02:50,500 --> 00:02:52,430
There was nothing left of his body.

49
00:02:54,579 --> 00:02:56,200
I'll kill you!

50
00:03:01,940 --> 00:03:02,820
Xiangjiu!

51
00:03:03,500 --> 00:03:04,260
Xiangjiu, are you alright?

52
00:03:04,260 --> 00:03:05,440
I'll kill you!

53
00:03:11,380 --> 00:03:12,620
Gongsun Hao!

54
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:16,980
Do you dare kill me?

55
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:22,430
I'm different from you.

56
00:03:23,180 --> 00:03:24,940
You're a cultivator.

57
00:03:25,700 --> 00:03:26,980
Once you take a life,

58
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:29,620
your body and soul
will be destroyed completely.

59
00:03:29,620 --> 00:03:31,540
No matter how many people I kill,

60
00:03:32,140 --> 00:03:34,020
as long as I put down my knife,

61
00:03:35,180 --> 00:03:37,460
I can achieve salvation.

62
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:09,220
You're merely a mortal.

63
00:04:31,420 --> 00:04:32,740
What's going on?

64
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:53,680
Master.

65
00:06:54,220 --> 00:06:55,820
If a cultivator takes a life,

66
00:06:56,100 --> 00:06:58,700
their body and soul
will be destroyed completely.

67
00:06:58,700 --> 00:06:59,900
I'm a loyal dog.

68
00:07:00,100 --> 00:07:01,100
I should be the one

69
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:03,210
doing this kind of thing of course.

70
00:07:39,100 --> 00:07:39,900
Mao Jin!

71
00:07:41,540 --> 00:07:42,340
Mao Jin.

72
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:45,340
Have you forgotten your aspiration?

73
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,840
Didn't you say you wanted
to guard the South Heavenly Gate

74
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,700
with Lord Howling Celestial Dog?

75
00:07:51,180 --> 00:07:51,980
You're...

76
00:07:52,980 --> 00:07:54,340
my South Heavenly Gate.

77
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,600
Master.

78
00:08:03,020 --> 00:08:04,420
Now I finally understand

79
00:08:05,740 --> 00:08:08,540
what Lord Howling Celestial Dog
has been guarding

80
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,680
is perhaps never that gate.

81
00:08:21,100 --> 00:08:22,140
Bai Yu,

82
00:08:22,780 --> 00:08:24,100
did you see that?

83
00:08:25,220 --> 00:08:26,260
My master...

84
00:08:27,220 --> 00:08:29,100
never killed your ancestors.

85
00:08:45,660 --> 00:08:46,460
Master.

86
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:50,220
I didn't let you down, did I?

87
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:53,460
I really am a loyal dog, right?

88
00:08:59,820 --> 00:09:01,300
You are my family.

89
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,120
Whose dog is this?

90
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,500
I'll beat you to death!

91
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:29,800
Thank you.

92
00:10:32,620 --> 00:10:34,080
Why are you here all alone?

93
00:10:35,300 --> 00:10:36,380
What's your name?

94
00:10:38,220 --> 00:10:40,340
You look a lot
like the Howling Celestial Dog.

95
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:41,020
From now on,

96
00:10:41,020 --> 00:10:42,550
would you like to follow me?

97
00:10:43,780 --> 00:10:44,710
Don't be afraid.

98
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:46,060
I'm here with you.

99
00:10:55,660 --> 00:10:56,460
Mao Jin,

100
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,900
you're unbelievable.

101
00:10:57,900 --> 00:10:59,080
Of course!

102
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:01,080
I'm unquestionably a loyal dog!

103
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:04,380
You really are a lackey.

104
00:11:04,380 --> 00:11:05,060
Yes.

105
00:11:05,420 --> 00:11:07,420
That's the highest praise for me.

106
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:10,920
So tell me,

107
00:11:11,420 --> 00:11:13,020
what's so great about your love?

108
00:11:13,020 --> 00:11:14,140
My love

109
00:11:14,260 --> 00:11:15,790
expects nothing in return.

110
00:11:15,980 --> 00:11:18,940
As long as she's happy, I'm happy.

111
00:11:19,020 --> 00:11:21,100
As long as she's well, I'm well too.

112
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:23,480
Just like how I treat my master.

113
00:11:35,460 --> 00:11:37,520
But I don't know how to sample dishes.

114
00:11:38,540 --> 00:11:40,740
There's nothing difficult about that.

115
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,840
Just take a bite of each dish,

116
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:45,610
and if you find something you like,
eat your fill.

117
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:01,180
Your Majesty,

118
00:12:01,700 --> 00:12:02,980
the remaining followers of Prince Fuying

119
00:12:02,980 --> 00:12:05,300
who should be handled have been handled.

120
00:12:06,040 --> 00:12:07,720
Tell them

121
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:10,300
not to expand the scope of punishment,

122
00:12:10,300 --> 00:12:12,300
to avoid implicating the innocent.

123
00:12:12,860 --> 00:12:14,500
Punish the principal offenders severely,

124
00:12:14,500 --> 00:12:17,620
the others leniently, or not at all.

125
00:12:17,620 --> 00:12:19,260
Your Majesty, you're wise.

126
00:12:20,420 --> 00:12:21,500
Where is Mochen?

127
00:12:22,660 --> 00:12:24,780
He still refuses to see me.

128
00:12:24,780 --> 00:12:25,980
Lord Feng said

129
00:12:26,300 --> 00:12:29,340
the bond between you and him has ended.

130
00:12:29,740 --> 00:12:31,900
There is no need to meet again.

131
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:47,780
If he stays here,

132
00:12:49,500 --> 00:12:52,030
will he really suffer tribulation
every day?

133
00:12:56,860 --> 00:12:57,990
Three days from now,

134
00:12:59,260 --> 00:13:00,540
unless he can ascend,

135
00:13:01,900 --> 00:13:02,700
otherwise...

136
00:13:03,700 --> 00:13:05,160
for the rest of his life...

137
00:13:06,220 --> 00:13:08,350
he will suffer tribulation every day.

138
00:13:27,220 --> 00:13:28,180
This isn't fair.

139
00:13:29,860 --> 00:13:30,790
This isn't fair.

140
00:13:32,980 --> 00:13:34,700
Why must he suffer all this?

141
00:13:39,300 --> 00:13:40,180
He is a demon.

142
00:13:41,460 --> 00:13:44,520
This is the price a demon must pay
to become an immortal.

143
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:46,040
What is a demon?

144
00:13:47,940 --> 00:13:49,670
If we're talking about demons,

145
00:13:50,380 --> 00:13:52,100
Gongsun Hao is the real demon.

146
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:54,020
You're right.

147
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:56,920
But his origin

148
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,520
is his original sin.

149
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:05,460
If he doesn't want
to accept fate's arrangement

150
00:14:05,880 --> 00:14:08,140
and live his life like all other animals,

151
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:10,400
he must endure these hardships.

152
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,400
You think this is unfair.

153
00:14:14,980 --> 00:14:17,580
But if anyone
could easily become an immortal,

154
00:14:19,300 --> 00:14:21,030
do you think that would be fair?

155
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,890
Now you have only 2 choices.

156
00:14:26,940 --> 00:14:28,270
Either help him ascend,

157
00:14:30,100 --> 00:14:32,300
or let him stay and suffer tribulation.

158
00:14:41,160 --> 00:14:42,560
Old Fox, you're back.

159
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:45,840
I've tidied up the Fucang Palace nicely.

160
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:47,760
That bastard Gongsun Hao

161
00:14:47,760 --> 00:14:49,800
made this place a complete mess.

162
00:14:51,360 --> 00:14:53,040
I have something to tell you.

163
00:14:57,260 --> 00:14:58,180
Wait a moment.

164
00:14:58,700 --> 00:15:00,940
Let me go light some incense first.

165
00:15:01,400 --> 00:15:02,360
I've been so busy lately...

166
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,890
I've decided not to ascend.

167
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:07,700
Why?

168
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,460
Actually,

169
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:13,450
after enduring so many tribulations,

170
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:15,200
I've gotten used to it.

171
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,930
It's not as painful as you imagine.

172
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:30,860
But I've never thought about
spending the rest of my life with you.

173
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:34,820
You can call me a coward,

174
00:15:35,260 --> 00:15:36,660
or say I'm heartless.

175
00:15:37,660 --> 00:15:38,500
In short,

176
00:15:39,620 --> 00:15:41,300
I don't have the courage

177
00:15:41,700 --> 00:15:43,500
to entrust the rest of my life...

178
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:46,320
to a fox.

179
00:15:49,780 --> 00:15:51,540
Actually, being with you before

180
00:15:51,540 --> 00:15:53,520
was merely out of novelty.

181
00:15:55,100 --> 00:15:56,500
In life,

182
00:15:57,380 --> 00:15:58,740
how many people

183
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:01,420
get to encounter a fox?

184
00:16:02,460 --> 00:16:03,780
But as time goes on,

185
00:16:04,280 --> 00:16:06,480
I would also inexplicably feel on edge.

186
00:16:07,140 --> 00:16:07,900
I'm worried

187
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:11,300
that I might accidentally
say something to anger you,

188
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:14,680
and you...

189
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:16,800
would eat me.

190
00:16:21,460 --> 00:16:23,000
I am human after all.

191
00:16:25,220 --> 00:16:27,150
In the future, I will marry a human.

192
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:30,340
I want to live with a human,

193
00:16:33,580 --> 00:16:35,540
not a fox.

194
00:16:39,900 --> 00:16:41,060
In this world,

195
00:16:42,260 --> 00:16:44,280
love that lasts a lifetime

196
00:16:46,100 --> 00:16:47,430
is already rare enough.

197
00:16:52,820 --> 00:16:54,440
But if that's the case,

198
00:16:56,340 --> 00:16:58,280
love that lasts every lifetime—

199
00:17:00,260 --> 00:17:03,190
wouldn't that be the greatest blessing
in the world?

200
00:17:05,180 --> 00:17:07,980
That's something
I wouldn't even dare to dream of.

201
00:17:09,339 --> 00:17:11,000
In my life,

202
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:15,540
if I could meet someone who loves me
for a lifetime, that would be enough.

203
00:17:17,079 --> 00:17:18,740
Wouldn't it be better

204
00:17:19,700 --> 00:17:21,359
if it were for every lifetime?

205
00:17:22,380 --> 00:17:24,640
You really don't understand love at all.

206
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:27,420
Getting love that lasts a lifetime

207
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:30,120
is already a rare blessing.

208
00:17:36,580 --> 00:17:38,360
If that's the case,

209
00:17:38,360 --> 00:17:41,900
if one could experience love
that lasts every lifetime,

210
00:17:42,460 --> 00:17:45,380
wouldn't that be the greatest blessing
in the world?

211
00:17:45,380 --> 00:17:47,260
Every lifetime?

212
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:52,600
That's something
I wouldn't even dare to dream of.

213
00:17:59,140 --> 00:18:01,070
Let's just consider each other...

214
00:18:02,780 --> 00:18:04,740
as mere passersby in life.

215
00:18:08,580 --> 00:18:09,380
Xiangjiu,

216
00:18:09,660 --> 00:18:10,740
the meal is ready!

217
00:18:12,340 --> 00:18:13,140
Wily Fox,

218
00:18:13,540 --> 00:18:14,470
you're here too.

219
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:16,560
If I had known,
I'd have had the Imperial Kitchen

220
00:18:16,560 --> 00:18:17,960
prepare chicken for you.

221
00:18:19,560 --> 00:18:21,000
He will soon ascend to immortality.

222
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:22,600
He must have many things to attend to.

223
00:18:22,600 --> 00:18:24,530
We shouldn't disturb him anymore.

224
00:18:28,540 --> 00:18:30,020
Look at your clothes.

225
00:18:30,180 --> 00:18:31,780
They're so improperly worn,

226
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,420
always askew like this.

227
00:18:33,420 --> 00:18:34,140
Alright.

228
00:18:34,140 --> 00:18:35,060
Got it.

229
00:18:35,660 --> 00:18:36,340
No.

230
00:18:36,340 --> 00:18:37,860
I must punish you this time.

231
00:18:37,860 --> 00:18:38,660
How?

232
00:18:41,340 --> 00:18:42,540
Carry me on your back.

233
00:19:32,100 --> 00:19:34,030
Why must you torment him like this?

234
00:19:35,140 --> 00:19:36,100
Only in this way

235
00:19:37,380 --> 00:19:39,460
can he leave without attachments.

236
00:19:43,780 --> 00:19:44,580
Ningshuang.

237
00:19:54,620 --> 00:19:55,380
Bai Yu,

238
00:19:56,020 --> 00:19:58,680
we shouldn't
see each other again in the future.

239
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:00,410
Ningshuang,

240
00:20:00,740 --> 00:20:01,980
this is my fault.

241
00:20:02,360 --> 00:20:03,840
If he loves me,

242
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:06,000
even without you,

243
00:20:06,680 --> 00:20:07,940
he would still love me.

244
00:20:09,260 --> 00:20:10,860
If he doesn't love me,

245
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:12,960
even without you,

246
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:16,080
he still wouldn't love me.

247
00:20:16,080 --> 00:20:16,880
Xiangjiu,

248
00:20:17,520 --> 00:20:19,920
I've had feelings for you since childhood.

249
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,900
That has not changed even now.

250
00:20:22,320 --> 00:20:23,380
But what about you?

251
00:20:24,720 --> 00:20:26,650
Have you ever felt anything for me?

252
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:28,160
In this world,

253
00:20:28,760 --> 00:20:31,490
there are always many things
beyond human power.

254
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:35,500
We call this helplessness and regret...

255
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:37,960
fate.

256
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:41,120
After Old Fox ascends,

257
00:20:41,360 --> 00:20:42,720
I will leave the palace

258
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:43,160
and live in seclusion in the countryside.

259
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:44,760
Then what does that make me?

260
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:47,520
He will be with me

261
00:20:47,520 --> 00:20:49,250
only because you won't be here.

262
00:20:49,600 --> 00:20:49,960
Well,

263
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:52,640
that makes me seem too cheap.

264
00:20:54,060 --> 00:20:55,100
This kind of love—

265
00:20:55,860 --> 00:20:57,100
I don't want it at all.

266
00:20:58,280 --> 00:21:00,080
You know that's not what I meant.

267
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:02,640
I know you mean well,

268
00:21:03,040 --> 00:21:04,600
but to me, love

269
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:07,440
is just like one of the 4 limbs.

270
00:21:07,760 --> 00:21:08,820
Limbs, once severed,

271
00:21:08,820 --> 00:21:10,080
can hardly grow back.

272
00:21:10,460 --> 00:21:12,000
But if I lose someone I love,

273
00:21:13,080 --> 00:21:14,540
I can simply find another.

274
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:16,640
There's no need to torment myself,

275
00:21:16,640 --> 00:21:18,520
much less to seek death.

276
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:20,760
In this world,

277
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:23,480
the only ones who will remain true to you

278
00:21:24,280 --> 00:21:25,410
are your parents...

279
00:21:26,800 --> 00:21:27,680
and yourself.

280
00:21:30,120 --> 00:21:31,600
Living in this world,

281
00:21:31,760 --> 00:21:33,600
why must we live so miserably?

282
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:36,040
When you're in love,
confess your feelings boldly.

283
00:21:36,040 --> 00:21:37,100
No need to be timid.

284
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:38,840
When you part,

285
00:21:39,360 --> 00:21:40,820
wave goodbye decisively,

286
00:21:41,560 --> 00:21:42,760
leaving no regrets.

287
