594
00:42:44,060 --> 00:42:45,900
How dare you!

595
00:42:46,020 --> 00:42:46,820
How insolent!

596
00:42:46,820 --> 00:42:48,660
You show no respect
for the higher immortals!

597
00:42:48,660 --> 00:42:49,940
You impudent little demon,

598
00:42:49,940 --> 00:42:51,620
how dare you say such outrageous words!

599
00:42:51,620 --> 00:42:52,940
Am I wrong?

600
00:42:53,700 --> 00:42:55,580
When the weak are bullied,

601
00:42:55,820 --> 00:42:56,900
where are you?

602
00:42:57,460 --> 00:42:59,740
When the sick suffer in pain,

603
00:43:00,460 --> 00:43:01,620
where are you?

604
00:43:02,860 --> 00:43:04,500
When parents lose their children,

605
00:43:04,500 --> 00:43:05,580
where are you?

606
00:43:05,980 --> 00:43:08,220
When evil people
trample the good underfoot,

607
00:43:08,220 --> 00:43:09,460
where are you?

608
00:43:11,460 --> 00:43:14,860
Since you never care about the suffering
in the mortal world,

609
00:43:15,580 --> 00:43:17,360
aren't you utterly worthless?

610
00:43:17,900 --> 00:43:20,420
